Vice President and Chief Sales Officer from June 2015 to December 2020 and Senior Vice President, Worldwide Sales
from May 2014 to June 2015. He was head of worldwide sales at LSI Corporation from 2010 until its acquisition by us
in 2014. He held several executive leadership positions at LSI from 2007 to 2010, including Vice President of Sales and
Marketing for the networking division and Vice President of Marketing for the networking and storage products group.
He was also the leader of Product Line Management for the Optical Ethernet and Multi-service Edge portfolio at Nortel
Networks Corporation prior to joining LSI.
