as our Chief Financial Officer from October 2016 to December 2020, Vice President and acting Chief Financial Officer
from March 2016 to October 2016 and Vice President of Corporate Development from January 2012 to March 2016. He
founded a financial advisory firm where he represented public and private technology companies from 2010 to 2012.
He was Vice President of Business Development at Techwell, Inc. from 2007 until its acquisition by Intersil Corporation
in 2010. He also held several roles at Technology Crossover Ventures and Robertson Stephens prior to joining
Techwell.
