6. Leases
At the beginning of fiscal year 2020, we adopted ASU 2016-02, Leases (“Topic 842”) using the optional adoption
method, whereby no adjustment to the financial statements of comparative periods was required. We have operating
and finance leases for our facilities, data centers and certain equipment. Operating lease expense was $102 million,
$106 million and $244 million for fiscal years 2021, 2020 and 2019, respectively. Finance lease expense was
$16 million and $14 million for fiscal years 2021 and 2020, respectively.
