Purchase Commitments. Represents unconditional purchase obligations that include agreements to purchase
goods or services, primarily inventory, that are enforceable and legally binding on us and that specify all significant
terms, including fixed or minimum quantities to be purchased, fixed, minimum or variable price provisions, and the
approximate timing of the transaction. Purchase obligations exclude agreements that are cancelable without penalty.
